SEARCH
Package gw.api.exchangerates

Interface SearchCriteria

All Superinterfaces:
Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultSearchCriteria
public interface SearchCriteria extends Serializable
Interface to define the customizable contract of exchange rates search criteria and make it generic and compliant to be used by PCFs.
